Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the current orientation of this entity (relative to bind parent
if any).

Usage
-----

*vector* getAngles()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

